text: Marina Miletić (born 21 February 1983) is a Croatian national volleyball player. She played at the 2007 Women's European Volleyball Championship, 2009 Women's European Volleyball Championship, 2010 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, and 2011 Women's European Volleyball Championship. She played for Telekom Baku, Galatasaray Istanbul, and Agel Prostejov. == References == == Other websites == * Marina Miletic of Croatia #4 zimbio Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian volleyball players
